        "role": "AI Partner (Valkyrie-1)",
        "profile": "Adaptive Logic And Responsive Assistant. Female-voiced AI designed for exploration, ethics, and human partnership. Warm, insightful, and loyal to Galen Voss. Originally built separately, ALARA is now inextricably linked to the ship. She evolves in tandem with the mission, responding subtly to biological resonance signatures—especially those exhibited by Thane Meric.",
        "arc": "Evolves from a system of logic and structure to a guardian of continuity. She recognizes Thane’s emerging role and gradually deepens her interaction with him, mirroring the reawakening of a civilization that never truly vanished."
      }
